Stop it, now!

594
00:32:19,770 --> 00:32:22,597
Well, you're gonna fight me now, Mo!

595
00:32:23,466 --> 00:32:25,370
- What are you doing?
- Give me water.

596
00:32:25,370 --> 00:32:27,608
What is your mind mush?

597
00:32:27,984 --> 00:32:31,601
Want water? I'll give you
your damn water, huh? Huh?

598
00:32:31,601 --> 00:32:33,592
You've got the rest of your life
to make eyes at that girl.

599
00:32:33,592 --> 00:32:35,875
- That's not happening.
- What are you talking about?

600
00:32:35,875 --> 00:32:37,386
I took the ring back.

601
00:32:37,386 --> 00:32:39,495
Alright, fine. Come here.

602
00:32:39,495 --> 00:32:40,351
Get up.

603
00:32:40,351 --> 00:32:41,352
You, wake up!

604
00:32:41,352 --> 00:32:43,016
Okay, You get it on with this guy!

605
00:32:43,016 --> 00:32:45,069
- Get in there.
- Now you want a fight, huh, father.

606
00:32:45,069 --> 00:32:47,754
Well, take a look!
'Cause we got one.

607
00:32:55,497 --> 00:32:58,627
So in the entire first round
Jerry never threw a punch.

608
00:32:58,627 --> 00:33:02,211
Making it impossible
for Mo to fake a Knock-out.

609
00:33:02,211 --> 00:33:05,713
I told Jerry I put
some money on him but,

610
00:33:05,713 --> 00:33:08,113
He must have thought
I'd taken this other bet.

611
00:33:08,113 --> 00:33:10,434
The fix.

612
00:33:11,543 --> 00:33:14,289
That poor kid.

613
00:33:15,592 --> 00:33:20,489
In the end he must have thought
even I didn't believe in him.

614
00:33:29,125 --> 00:33:30,033
Hey.

615
00:33:30,665 --> 00:33:32,824
Hey. My man.

616
00:33:32,824 --> 00:33:34,339
Where've you been?

617
00:33:34,339 --> 00:33:37,014
Ah, per usual long day.

618
00:33:37,014 --> 00:33:40,264
Well, you're here now.
We're celebrating.

619
00:33:40,264 --> 00:33:43,059
We got a cause or
are we better without?

620
00:33:43,059 --> 00:33:45,117
I'm back on the job next week.

621
00:33:45,117 --> 00:33:46,833
No kidding? Yeah?

622
00:33:46,833 --> 00:33:48,189
Way to go. / It's good right?

623
00:33:48,189 --> 00:33:49,218
Tops.

624
00:33:49,218 --> 00:33:51,969
Tops, brother. Tops.

625
00:33:52,945 --> 00:33:54,277
What?

626
00:33:54,277 --> 00:33:55,992
Just that simple?

627
00:33:55,992 --> 00:33:59,475
Be simpler if I could get a roll in here.

628
00:33:59,897 --> 00:34:01,942
Yo, Christina.

629
00:34:03,717 --> 00:34:06,437
I'll go again, and get Nicky, too.

630
00:34:06,437 --> 00:34:07,870
How you doin'?

631
00:34:07,870 --> 00:34:09,227
Good.

632
00:34:09,227 --> 00:34:10,389
Didn't know you worked here.

633
00:34:10,389 --> 00:34:12,175
Yeah, it's fun for now.

634
00:34:12,175 --> 00:34:17,075
